description.narrative:
Overall Objective: The overall objective of the program is to empower and encourage communities to actively participate in monitoring of infrastructure sector to increase transparency and accountability and therefrom improve the quality of Infrastructure projects
Specific objectives: - Improved capabilities of local communities and selected local state institutions to engage in enhancing integrity in service delivery in education, health, transportation, water and sanitation infrastructure projects in 4 provinces in Afghanistan.
- Improved responsiveness of public service providers at local level by engaging local communities and key state institutions in joint, collaborative forums and working groups for regular and systematic assessment of CIB policies and integrity in service delivery. ;
